org.cef.callback

Interface CefContextMenuParams


  • public interface CefContextMenuParams
    Provides information about the context menu state. The methods of this class can only be accessed on browser process the UI thread.(提供有关上下文菜单状态的信息。此类的方法只能在浏览器进程UI线程上访问。)

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  CefContextMenuParams.EditStateFlags
      Supported context menu edit state bit flags.(支持的上下文菜单编辑状态位标志。)
      static class  CefContextMenuParams.MediaStateFlags
      Supported context menu media state bit flags.(支持的上下文菜单媒体状态位标志。)
      static class  CefContextMenuParams.MediaType
      Supported context menu media types.(支持的上下文菜单媒体类型。)
      static class  CefContextMenuParams.TypeFlags
      Supported context menu type flags.(支持的上下文菜单类型标志。)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean getDictionarySuggestions(java.util.Vector<java.lang.String> suggestions)
      Returns true if suggestions exist, false otherwise.(如果存在建议，则返回true，否则返回false。)
      int getEditStateFlags()
      Returns flags representing the actions supported by the editable node, if any, that the context menu was invoked on.(返回表示可编辑节点支持的操作的标志（如果有的话），该可编辑节点调用了上下文菜单。)
      java.lang.String getFrameCharset()
      Returns the character encoding of the subframe that the context menu was invoked on.(返回调用上下文菜单的子框架的字符编码。)
      java.lang.String getFrameUrl()
      Returns the URL of the subframe that the context menu was invoked on.(返回调用上下文菜单的子框架的URL。)
      java.lang.String getLinkUrl()
      Returns the URL of the link, if any, that encloses the node that the context menu was invoked on.(返回链接的URL（如果有），该链接包含调用上下文菜单的节点。)
      int getMediaStateFlags()
      Returns flags representing the actions supported by the media element, if any, that the context menu was invoked on.(返回表示调用上下文菜单的媒体元素（如果有的话）支持的操作的标志。)
      CefContextMenuParams.MediaType getMediaType()
      Returns the type of context node that the context menu was invoked on.(返回调用上下文菜单的上下文节点的类型。)
      java.lang.String getMisspelledWord()
      Returns the text of the misspelled word, if any, that the context menu was invoked on.(返回调用上下文菜单时拼写错误的单词（如果有的话）的文本。)
      java.lang.String getPageUrl()
      Returns the URL of the top level page that the context menu was invoked on.(返回调用上下文菜单的顶级页面的URL。)
      java.lang.String getSelectionText()
      Returns the text of the selection, if any, that the context menu was invoked on.(返回调用上下文菜单时所选内容的文本（如果有的话）。)
      java.lang.String getSourceUrl()
      Returns the source URL, if any, for the element that the context menu was invoked on.(返回调用上下文菜单的元素的源URL（如果有的话）。)
      int getTypeFlags()
      Returns flags representing the type of node that the context menu was invoked on.(返回表示调用上下文菜单的节点类型的标志。)
      java.lang.String getUnfilteredLinkUrl()
      Returns the link URL, if any, to be used ONLY for "copy link address".(返回链接URL（如果有），仅用于“复制链接地址”。)
      int getXCoord()
      Returns the X coordinate of the mouse where the context menu was invoked.(返回调用上下文菜单的鼠标的X坐标。)
      int getYCoord()
      Returns the Y coordinate of the mouse where the context menu was invoked.(返回调用上下文菜单的鼠标的Y坐标。)
      boolean hasImageContents()
      Returns true if the context menu was invoked on an image which has non-empty contents.(如果上下文菜单是在具有非空内容的图像上调用的，则返回true。)
      boolean isEditable()
      Returns true if the context menu was invoked on an editable node.(如果上下文菜单是在可编辑节点上调用的，则返回true。)
      boolean isSpellCheckEnabled()
      Returns true if the context menu was invoked on an editable node where spell-check is enabled.(如果在启用拼写检查的可编辑节点上调用上下文菜单，则返回true。)

    • Method Detail

      • getDictionarySuggestions

        boolean getDictionarySuggestions(java.util.Vector<java.lang.String> suggestions)
        Returns true if suggestions exist, false otherwise. Fills in |suggestions| from the spell check service for the misspelled word if there is one.(如果存在建议，则返回true，否则返回false。从拼写检查服务中为拼写错误的单词填写 |suggestions|（如果有的话）。)

      • getEditStateFlags

        int getEditStateFlags()
        Returns flags representing the actions supported by the editable node, if any, that the context menu was invoked on. See EditStateFlags for possible values.(返回表示可编辑节点支持的操作的标志（如果有的话），该可编辑节点调用了上下文菜单。有关可能的值，请参阅EditStateFlags。)

      • getSourceUrl

        java.lang.String getSourceUrl()
        Returns the source URL, if any, for the element that the context menu was invoked on. Example of elements with source URLs are img, audio, and video.(返回调用上下文菜单的元素的源URL（如果有的话）。具有源URL的元素示例：img、audio和video。)

      • getTypeFlags

        int getTypeFlags()
        Returns flags representing the type of node that the context menu was invoked on. See TypeFlags for supported values(返回表示调用上下文菜单的节点类型的标志。有关支持的值，请参阅TypeFlags)

      • getUnfilteredLinkUrl

        java.lang.String getUnfilteredLinkUrl()
        Returns the link URL, if any, to be used ONLY for "copy link address". We don't validate this field in the frontend process.(返回链接URL（如果有），仅用于“复制链接地址”。我们不会在前端过程中验证此字段。)

      • getXCoord

        int getXCoord()
        Returns the X coordinate of the mouse where the context menu was invoked. Coords are relative to the associated RenderView's origin.(返回调用上下文菜单的鼠标的X坐标。坐标是相对于关联的RenderView的原点的。)

      • getYCoord

        int getYCoord()
        Returns the Y coordinate of the mouse where the context menu was invoked. Coords are relative to the associated RenderView's origin.(返回调用上下文菜单的鼠标的Y坐标。坐标是相对于关联的RenderView的原点的。)

      • isEditable

      • isSpellCheckEnabled
